node.name: v_crime
node.raw_sql:
SELECT
  unique_key,
  address,
  census_tract,
  clearance_date,
  clearance_status,
  council_district_code,
  description,
  district,
  latitude,
  longitude,
  location,
  location_description,
  primary_type,
  timestamp,
  x_coordinate,
  y_coordinate,
  year,
  zipcode
FROM
  `dw-test-01-229320.dbt_prototype.crime`
LIMIT
  1000
